==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Trotter
<hw>Trot"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One that
trots; especially, a horse trained to be driven in trotting
matches.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The foot of an animal, especially that of a sheep;
also, humorously, the human foot.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trottoir</ent>⟦br⟧
